<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org"
	xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head th:replace="pay/common/common :: head"></head>

<body>
	<!-- header -->
	<div class="header">
		<img src="/assets/images/web/logo.png" class="cache" >
		<img src="/assets/images/server.png" class="cache" >
		<div class="content fixed-width">
			<div class="tools" th:if="false">
				<a th:href="${'/pay/query_' + type + '/'+ uuid}" data-tooltip-title="点击前往查询订单信息">订单查询</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<!-- header End-->
	

	<!-- container -->
	<div class="container">
		<div class="content-des font-red des-1">
			<p>注：所有充值业务全及时生效(网络高峰期5-10分钟等待)，充值完成以后,请您在指定NPC处领取.无需向管理员索取。</p>
		</div>

		<div class="pay-body">
			<div class="order">
				<h2>我要留言</h2>
				<form id="form-data">
					<dl>
						<dd>
		                    <span class="lab">游戏分区：</span>
	                        <select class="form-control required" id="partition" name="partitionId" data-rule="{required: true}" style="width: 214px;height: 32px;">
		        				<option th:if="${!#lists.isEmpty(list) and #lists.size(list) != 1}" value="">--请选择分区--</option>
		        				
	       						<option th:if="${!#lists.isEmpty(list)}" th:each="item:${list}" 
	       							th:value="${item.id}" th:text="${item.name}"></option>
	                        </select>
	                        <strong class="font-error">&nbsp;*</strong>
		                </dd>
					</dl>
					<dl>
						<dd>
							<span class="lab">游戏帐号：</span>
							<input class="form-control required" maxlength="30" name="account" data-rule="{required: true}" type="text" placeholder="请输入您的游戏账号">
							<strong class="font-error">&nbsp;*</strong>
						</dd>
					</dl>
					<dl>
						<dd>
							<span class="lab">联系ＱＱ：</span>
							<input class="form-control required" maxlength="11" name="qq" data-rule="{qqnumber: false}" type="text" placeholder="请输入您的联系QQ">
						</dd>
					</dl>
					<dl>
						<dd>
							<span class="lab">联系电话：</span>
							<input class="form-control required" maxlength="11" name="phone" data-rule="{phonenumber: false}" type="text" placeholder="请输入您的联系电话">
						</dd>
					</dl>
					<dl>
		                <dd>
		                    <span class="lab">留言内容：</span>
		                    <textarea class="form-control required" name="content" data-rule="{required: true}" style="width:300px; height:90px;" rows="5" maxlength="100" placeholder="请输入您的留言内容"></textarea>
		                    <strong class="font-error">&nbsp;*</strong>
		                </dd>
					</dl>
	 				<dl>
	 					<dd>
	 						<span class="lab">&nbsp;</span>
		 					<a id="form-commit" href="javascript:;" class="btn" title="点击提交留言">确定留言</a>
	 					</dd>
	 				</dl>
				</form>
			</div>
			<div class="des-remark">
				<p>注意：请玩家在确认成功冲值后，假如还没有出现获得相关物品，请再等几分钟，然后再用您充值的游戏帐号登陆，进行查看！谢谢！！</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<!-- container End-->
	
	<!-- foot -->
	<div th:replace="pay/common/common :: foot"></div>
	<!-- foot End-->
	
	<!-- online-server -->
	<div th:replace="pay/common/common :: online-server"></div>
	<!-- online-server End-->
	
	<!-- script-IE -->
	<div th:replace="pay/common/common :: script-ie"></div>
	<!-- script-IE End-->
	
	<script type="text/javascript" src="/assets/js/recharge.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript">
		$(function() {
			$.message();
		});
	</script>
</body>
</html>
